items.description: Found during the quest "Amulets of Night Power." While wearing the Amulet, the summoned Gargoyle spell will summon an additional gargoyle for 30 seconds.

items.name: Andurs' Amulet of Arkay
items.description: Located in the catacombs of the Hall of the Dead in Whiterun, in the northern most room. Increases your health by 10 points.

items.name: Charmed Necklace
items.description: Given to the Dragonborn by the randomly-encountered Revelers in exchange for a bottle of Honningbrew Mead. Carry capacity increased by 25 (can also be taken from their dead bodies).

items.name: The Gauldur Amulet
items.description: Obtained by completing the "Forbidden Legend" quest chain, and grants +30 to Health, Magicka, and Stamina.

items.name: Kyne's Token
items.description: Received after completing the quest "Kyne's Sacred Trials." Damage taken from animals is reduced by 10%, and bows do 5% more damage against animals.

items.name: Locket of Saint Jiub
items.description: Given to the Dragonborn after completing "Impatience of a Saint" quest for Jiub, a spirit in the Soul Cairn. It increases stamina and carrying capacity by 50 points each.

items.name: Necromancer's Amulet
items.description: Obtained by looting Calixto's corpse at the end of "Blood on the Ice" (if it was sold to him before). +50 magicka, Conjuration spells cost 25% less to cast, and Health and Stamina regenerate 75% lower.

items.name: Reyda's Necklace
items.description: Obtained during "The Straw that Broke."

items.name: Saarthal Amulet
items.description: Found during the quest "Under Saarthal." Spells in all schools cost 3% less to cast.

items.name: Savos Aren's Amulet
items.description: Obtained by completing the quest "Containment." Increases maximum magicka by 50.

items.name: Strange Amulet
items.description: Found during the quest "Blood on the Ice."

items.name: Yisra's Necklace
items.description: Found on Yisra's corpse, which can be found at Yisra's Beachside Combustion.

items.name: Asgeir's Wedding Band
items.description: Found during Dark Brotherhood quest "Bound Until Death" on the body of Asgeir Snow-Shod.

items.name: Balwen's Ornamental Ring
items.description: Obtained during "Daedric Relic."

items.name: The Bond of Matrimony
items.description: Received upon completing "The Bonds of Matrimony" and getting married. Restoration spells cost 10% less to cast.

items.name: Enchanted Ring
items.description: Multiples of this ring are found during the College of Winterhold quest "Under Saarthal." Increases maximum health by 20.

items.name: Fjola's Wedding Band
items.description: Received during the quest "Forgetting about Fjola."

items.name: Katarina's Ornamental Ring
items.description: Obtained during "Daedric Relic."

items.name: Madesi's Silver Ring
items.description: Obtained during "A Chance Arrangement."

items.name: Muiri's Ring
items.description: Possible additional reward during the Dark Brotherhood quest "Mourning Never Comes." Alchemy is 15% better.

items.name: Nightweaver's Band
items.description: Possible additional reward during the Dark Brotherhood quest "Recipe for Disaster." Sneaking is 10% better, and Destruction spells cost 10% less to cast.

items.name: Pithi's Ornamental Ring
items.description: Obtained during "Daedric Relic."

items.name: Ring of Pure Mixtures
items.description: Obtained by the Dragonborn as part of a miscellaneous quest given by Frida in Dawnstar.

items.name: Ring of Hircine
items.description: Daedric artifact of Hircine. Possible reward from the quest "Ill Met by Moonlight." Allows unlimited transformations for Werewolves. One only needs to reequip it after returning to their original form.

items.name: Ring of Namira
items.description: Granted after the quest "The Taste of Death," grants the ability to feed on a dead corpse resulting in increase health, and health regeneration for a set time limit. +50 Stamina.

items.name: Ring of the Beast
items.description: Obtained during the quest "Rings of Blood Magic." Grants the user 100 extra health and a bonus 20 melee damage while in Vampire Lord form.

items.name: Ring of the Erudite
items.description: Obtained during the quest "Rings of Blood Magic." Grants the user 100 extra Magicka and a bonus magicka regeneration rate as a Vampire Lord.

items.name: Silver-Blood Family Ring
items.description: Possible reward from the quest "No One Escapes Cidhna Mine." Smithing is 15% better.

items.name: Treoy's Ornamental Ring
items.description: Obtained during "Daedric Relic."

items.name: Vittoria's Wedding Band
items.description: Found during Dark Brotherhood quest "Bound Until Death" on body of Vittoria Vici.

items.name: Viola's Gold Ring
items.description: Given to the Dragonborn during Revyn Sadri's miscellaneous quest.

items.name: Calcelmo's Ring
items.description: Kerah in Markarth asks the Dragonborn to deliver this ring to Calcelmo.

items.name: Ilas-Tei's Ring
items.description: Found north-northeast of Ysgramor's Tomb below a Shrine of Talos.
